---
// FAQ Section Component
---

<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>I'm not tech-savvy. Will this be too complicated?</h3>
        <p>Not at all. I handle all the technical work. You focus on running your business while I optimize your Google presence and website.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How long before I see more phone calls?</h3>
        <p>Google Business Profile improvements often show results within 30-60 days. Most clients see increased visibility and inquiries as optimizations take effect.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you work with my type of business?</h3>
        <p>I specialize in contractors, auto shops, cleaning services, landscaping, and pet businesses. These industries see the fastest results from local SEO.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What if I can't afford $1,500/month?</h3>
        <p>Start with the $497 Google Business Profile makeover. It delivers immediate results and you can upgrade to monthly services when ready.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can you track which calls come from Google?</h3>
        <p>Yes. I set up call tracking so you know exactly which marketing efforts are driving phone calls to your business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do I have to sign a long contract?</h3>
        <p>No contracts required. Monthly services are month-to-month. One-time projects like the Google Business Profile makeover have no ongoing commitment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* FAQ Section */
  .faq-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #FAFAFA;
  }
  
  .faq-section .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .faq-section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .faq-section .section-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
  }
  
  .faq-item {
    background: transparent;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: left;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-item {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .faq-item h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .faq-item p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  }
  
  .faq-item:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95));
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 87, 56, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>